### Car Higher API Test Suite
### Use with "REST Client" extension (Free & Open Source)

@baseUrl = http://localhost/Car_Higher

### 1. Get Vehicle GPS
# Fetches real-time position and history for a specific booking
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vehicle-gps.php?booking_id=1
Accept: application/json

###
### 2. Get Global Fleet Status
# Fetches current position of all active vehicles in the fleet
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fleet-gps.php
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Validate Voucher
# Validates a promo code against a specific booking amount
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/validate-voucher.php?code=RESCUE10&amount=500
Accept: application/json

###
### 4. Simulate GPS Step
# Manually advances a vehicle one step along the Lusaka route
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/simulate-step.php?booking_id=1
Accept: application/json
